sources.title: Bonanza (TV-1960) DARK STAR (S1E31)
sources.description:
This Timeless TV Western starring Lorne Green, Pernell Roberts, Dan Blocker and Michael Landon, is one of the most popular shows in television history!

DARK STAR: Joe is about to shoot what he thinks is a wolf that turns out to be a young gypsy woman. Tirzaza has been condemned to death by her people claiming she's a witch. She's brought to the Ponderosa where she and Joe fall in love. Joe goes about the task of explaining the strange happenings that are blamed on the woman.
